snippet.title: [Solo Leveling:ARISE] Ver 3.0 Update PV: Jeju Island Raid Revealed!  Battle against the Ant King!
snippet.description:
Ver 3.0 Update PV coming soon!
Jeju Island Raid Revealed! Battle against the worst magic beast, the King of the ants!

The Ant King’s shadow that will change Jeju Island into a land of death is approaching. 👑🐜
S-Rank hunters in danger! 
Become Sung Jinwoo himself and reclaim Jeju Island from the worst magic beast, the King of the ants!

👇 Have you pre-registered for the Jeju Island Raid? If not, tab the link below!
https://sololeveling.netmarble.com/beruupdate

💝 When pre-registering for the Jeju Island update pre-registration, Custom Draw Tickets will be obtainable!
Rate Up Draw Ticket, Lv. 78 Legendary Artifact Full Set, SSR Jinwoo Weapon Selection Ticket, and Update Celebration Sung Jinwoo Costume will be given based on the achieved pre-registrations.

────────────────────────

[Solo Leveling:ARISE]
There is always a next level in the game!

The global legendary Webtoon with 14.3 Billion views,
Solo Leveling is now a game!  
👉Play Now:  https://ntiny.link/sololeveling_official_us  

🎁Start now to get $150 worth of national-level rewards!🎁
🎮Play Now!🎮
